{"tid":99169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普新令：停收難民至少120天 嚴管7穆斯林國簽證","createTime":"2017-01-29T03:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T05:13:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5aa039cbf5ca78a413bc61c5433afafd924c60b","tid":99169,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>川普新令：停收難民至少120天 嚴管7穆斯林國簽證</strong><br />\n<br />\n更新時間 ： 2017-01-27 11:18 PM <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2017/1-28/p7975771a946238840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F1-28%2Fp7975771a946238840.jpg&h=0b39510d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Donald J. Trump 臉書)<br />\n<br />\n【新唐人2017年01月28日訊】美國總統川普今天在五角大廈簽下「阻止外國恐怖分子進入美國的國家保護計劃」全面性新行政命令，內容包括<strong>暫停收容難民至少120天</strong>，並對來自7個穆斯林國家的旅客新增嚴格管制措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n川普（Donald Trump）簽下行政命令後表示：「這是一件大事。」他說，他要讓美國遠離「激進伊斯蘭恐怖分子」、「我們只會接納支持和熱愛美國的人。」白宮尚未立即公佈命令內容。<br />\n<br />\n新行政命令包括完全停止收容難民至少120天，並利用這段期間制定嚴厲的全新審查措施。<strong>同時將2017年的接收移民上限設在5萬人</strong>&mdash;&mdash;這是原有上限的一半以下。<br />\n<br />\n川普也下令，<span style=\"color: red;\">未來30天不得核發簽證給伊朗、伊拉克、利比亞、索馬利亞、蘇丹、敘利亞與也門等7個穆斯林國家的移民及旅客。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於幼時就被帶到美國的非法移民、所謂的「追夢人」（Dreamers），川普稍早接受美國廣播公司新聞網（ABC News）專訪時說：「他們毋須太擔心。&hellip;我們會照顧每個人。」他還說：「來到這裡是很棒且表現出色的人，他們不用擔心那麼多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n專訪時，川普也表示，給予敘利亞難民身份時<span style=\"color: red;\">將優先給予基督徒</span>。但行政命令中暫時會禁止敘利亞難民入境，直至有「重大改變」才會取消禁令。<br />\n<br />\n川普這次批准的其他措施包括不再容許移民<strong>在沒有接受面試下續領簽證。</strong><br />\n<br />\n他亦簽署行政命令擴軍，制定方案建造新飛機﹑船隻﹑資源等等。<br />\n<br />\n(責任編輯：許惠安) <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2017/01/28/a1309081.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2Fa1309081.html&d=AqY7y7jJ%2FuWEOQGpCgMhp4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=97c1be92\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2017/01/28/a1309081.html</a>"},{"pid":"e12e040ab8e7fe4dbedf4dd249a2bbe37384adf3","tid":99169,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"trump trump we real trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72f2054af0c211ff83406641e6213dd0e1f58cf","tid":99169,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 伊斯蘭狗<br />\n咪撚將你嘅文化帶畀<br />\n非伊斯蘭教徒"},{"pid":"c70195a5069e5f43e451c19b5a48a17751f872de","tid":99169,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734d443829ffd61325a843f1f1583e6017d617fe","tid":99169,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d850cbe9a1fd6ef46b14c28b46b19d5bf041faf","tid":99169,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"香港無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9174f2cb1af56b4499bc333ff1e523bfcf86c12","tid":99169,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251df159da25890e27f925de381155479618826d","tid":99169,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"真本土"},{"pid":"1a54451e79e74420cf0f9e31d823c542e2c909f4","tid":99169,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"左膠又係時候發癲啦，侵侵好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e8ff4acf44f7d1a9